<div class="tab-panel">
  <ul class="nav nav-pills mb-3" id="pills-tab" role="tablist">
    <li class="nav-item">
      <a class="nav-link active" id="photo-tab" data-toggle="tab" href="#photo" role="tab" aria-controls="photo" aria-selected="true">Photos</a>
    </li>
    <li class="nav-item">
      <a class="nav-link" id="review-tab" data-toggle="tab" href="#review" role="tab" aria-controls="review" aria-selected="false">Reviews</a>
    </li>
    <li class="nav-item">
      <a class="nav-link" id="contact-tab" data-toggle="tab" href="#contact" role="tab" aria-controls="contact" aria-selected="false">Description</a>
    </li>
    <li class="nav-item">
      <a class="nav-link" id="menu-tab" data-toggle="tab" href="#menu" role="tab" aria-controls="menu" aria-selected="false">Menu</a>
    </li>
  </ul>
  <div class="tab-content" id="pills-tabContent">
    <div class="tab-pane fade show active" id="photo" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="photo-tab">
      <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Iure esse magni quasi, inventore similique expedita corrupti hic magnam illum nostrum mollitia, modi numquam at beatae ratione, vitae, obcaecati dolore! Earum.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="tab-pane fade" id="review" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="review-tab">
      <div class="row container">
        <% if !@restaurant.reviews.first.nil? %>
        <div class="col-6">
          <%= render "reviews/reviews" %>
        </div>
        <% end %>
        <div class="col-6">
           <%= render "shared/restaurant_review_form", class: "mt-4"%>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="tab-pane fade" id="contact" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="contact-tab">
      <%= @restaurant.description %>
    </div>
    <div class="tab-pane fade" id="menu" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="menu-tab">
      <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Provident quam aut, voluptatem modi quasi nemo a eum ipsa cupiditate, quis nobis libero voluptate doloribus, sunt in, et nihil. Atque, vitae?</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
